    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a project or a parts car. The engine currently starts but runs roughly and suffers from several noticeable fluid leaks that will need immediate attention. Visually, the body shows significant signs of age, including areas of rust on the lower panels and several dents. The interior is heavily worn, with some tears in the upholstery and non-functional electronics. It is recommended that the buyer hauls the vehicle rather than driving it away.",
