    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You have to see this beauty to believe it! I've honestly babied this car since day one, and it is in absolutely stunning, flawless condition. It looks and smells just like it did the day it left the showroom! It drives like a total dream and has been kept sparkling clean inside and out. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new but at a much better price, this is the one for you! Drop me a message\u2014I'd love to show it to you! \u2728",
      "price": 43500.0,
