      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a superlative E46 M3, a collector-grade example of the S54-powered icon. This 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six features a fully overhauled double-VANOS system and proactive rod bearing replacement to ensure peak high-revving reliability. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to the rear wheels via a Variable M Differential Lock. The chassis is structurally sound with documented rear subframe reinforcement. The suspension retains its factory geometry with fresh OEM bushings, providing the telepathic steering response characteristic of this chassis. Finished in Carbon Black with a flawless Nappa leather interior, the vehicle displays consistent paint meter readings across all panels and a factory-clean undercarriage. A mechanically sound, concourse-level specimen for the discerning purist.",
